metadata: {"name": "Tapuya DAO 1/80", "description": "Tapuya.xyz is about decentralizing cultural expression, preserving ancestral heritage, and empowering ethnic communities. As a symbol of ancestral futures, we created TAYI in collaboration with an AI agent. TAYI means "seed that has blossomed" in Guarani. The image was created from the combination of visual genes from various plants and animals. TAYI holders will seed the set up of Tapuya DAO, and have Founding roles in our Discord. We hope to have you with us. With love, Tapuya.
